@abirballan @HungryHorsie A vaccine won't make anyone clean.
I have a way to be sure and 
it is better than a cure.

@abirballan T-Detect by @AdaptiveBiotech was recently approved by FDA.  It is estimated to cost around $250 out-of-pocket.

FDA's caveat: a negative test "do not rule out acute or current SARS-CoV-2 infection."

